{
  "stem": "150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I immediately started working in that hospital, primarily because they had an ambulance that the Soviet POW who was the ambulance driver would let me drive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I enjoyed that very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And mostly, I didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I just lay around, you know, waiting to see what's going to happen next and reading books.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was much later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was much later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At first, I didn't really know what to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew my father was dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know if my mother was alive or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I decided I might as well go back home to Lithuania because I wanted to go to school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 14 and a half when I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew I was ignorant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't go to school in a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody was coming by from the different countries taking their citizens back to wherever they belonged.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Soviets wanted their citizens back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Much later, after I came to the States, I found out the Soviets not only were looking for them, they were demanding that they be turned over.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they blackmailed Stalin-- they blackmailed Churchill into making sure that all Soviet citizens are returned by force to be executed or imprisoned, or else Stalin wasn't going to give back the British POWs to the British.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I voluntarily went and registered to go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the time my transport was ready to go, I was waiting for it in Munich, and some people from the previous transport started running back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one guy came to us, and he said, hey, don't go because everybody gets put in a camp, and everybody goes before a commission.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody gets asked the same question.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
